HEADWORD: Hydrogenize
<hw>Hy"dro*gen*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Hydrogenized</conjf>
<pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos> <conjf>Hydrogenizing</conjf>
<pr>(?)</pr>.]</vmorph> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>To combine with
